content.description:
This climb is located in the Crimpshaft which is the narrow corridor leading north from the Crimpfest Wall (also a way to reach

Private Idaho

). Scramble up two tiers to a decent ledge inside of the corridor. Begin the climb on the west side (faces opposite of Crimpfest Wall) of the corridor. The climb starts up a strenuous roof followed by powerful climbing to a rest at an obvious, undercling handjam. Continue up more burly moves, and try to hang on as the climbing gets easier near the top - pumpy.
